Comment: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.10,Sign,,0,0,0,,{ep title}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You’re not coming home again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadlines keep piling up one after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Once I wrap things up, \NI’ll come straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been half a month since Kenji left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come home soon, Kenji you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Skit 35:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,, Temptations of Slavery. {誘惑のタコ部屋}{lit: takobeya of temptation/seduction - takobeya (literally "squid room") is https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Takobeya_labour - genuinely not sure what to title this episode this time}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you... go give this to Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... You should rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve got tons of work, so come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, when will I ever see Hikaru again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’ve got to hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t lose heart, Aoyama Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I brought the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is Sensei’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,most sacred smell! {????? *** nioi}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{goki - cockroach sounds}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so glad I became her apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my... {???? ara, ***}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cockroasted! {oshimai da goku - I'm done for, goki}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I don't know \Nwhat's gotten into me... {/it just happened on the spur of the moment}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s fine. Without a little depravity, \Nyou can’t draw a sensual manga. {lit: without that much ecchi, can't draw sexy manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This coffee is my special blend. \NHow many sugars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You look surprised—is it because \NI seem different from usual? {fun'iki = mood/atmosphere/airs}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it’s just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,I mean, at the office you’re always like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Clumsy! Useless! {???}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots should just go back to \Nwhatever neck of the woods you came from! {lit: to the countryside}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,...and that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I turn into a different person when I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone probably thinks I’m a horrible woman, \Nbut I just don’t want to publish half-baked work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That’s not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, work’s tough, \Nbut I really appreciate you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. \NYou’re a kind guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, \Ndo you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I do... {????????? not a clue what this sanda is, or what his answer might be, yes or no, the next lines don't make it clear}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama Kenji, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:03.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream—Egaki Rei herself \Ntreated me to a coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,And on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{? probably cat sounds?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I’m sticking with you for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as I master my craft... {???? no clue what he means: and then, learning the job fast}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Kenji. \NI missed you! {/I was lonely}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll do it, Hikaru. \NJust you wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama-san, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I’d like your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help? Mizuki-san, you're the chief \Nof the editorial team,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of help might you need \Nfrom a rookie like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mizuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m drawing a love scene, \Nbut I can’t get the feeling right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we try it out for real, I think I’ll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can’t be serious... {/even if you say so...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help me out, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.78,Note,,0,0,0,,[Parody of Ultraman's chant]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji, don’t do anything rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, Mizuki-san, I can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all for the sake of manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikaru, I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fired after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the hard work, Mizuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my storyboard. {"name" is manga slang for "storyboard; rough draft​" somehow}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The scene where a man who has a girlfriend \Ngets seduced by another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, does that mean what we just did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Mizuki-san\N to put on a little act for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can draw a realistic scene about \Nthe emotions of a man who has been seduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Y-You’ve got to be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?\NGet to drawing, chop-chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:12.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I never agreed to be part of this act! \NMaking a fool out of me... {lit: consent/understanding is no good - not sure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:17.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,What do we have here? \NA man gets seduced but doesn’t waver at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:22.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,He thinks of the girlfriend he loves \Nand rejects temptation without hesitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! No matter how in love you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if a sexy woman’s right in front of you, \Nyou take her! That’s how men are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I’ll wreck this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for making fun of me! \NA man always takes what he wants! {???? *** baka ni shita batsu da! yaritai you ni ***}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Change this, and this! And this too! \NHow about that?! {?????}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You rewrote my storyboard \Nwithout permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I can’t let you stay as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,This time, fired for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was short, but thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you said I was fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But this draft turned out \Neven better than originally intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:15.00,Song,,0,0,0,,{futari; 体につたわりキュンとなるのね\N指も唇ももっと知りたい\N明日も昨日もずっとふたりを Take me} I feel it deep inside, a spark running through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:23.04,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to know your fingers, your lips even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:28.35,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,555)}Tomorrow, yesterday, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re more than qualified \Nto be my full-fledged partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you’ll also draw manga \Nunder the name of Mutsumi Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, I’m finally debuting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?!
